DATA Extraction from YELP API

This project obtains data on local businesses and stores the data in a database. It uses YELP FUSION to pull real time data form YELP's 
open source API on local businesses and store the data in Postgres database.

Description of Project files

1. authorization.py - This file is used for making HTTP Request

2. business_searching.py - This file handles results from YELP search requests.

3. db_driver.py - This file is used to connect to the Postgres database and run the required queries.

4. drivers_queries.py - This file has the required queiries to create the database Schema in Postres.

5. API_request.py - This file makes request to the API.

6. driver.py - This file controls the program flow.

